"{\"uid\": \"www.beckershospitalreview.com.-finance-how-brexit-will-affect-american-healthcare-companies-4-thoughts-html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Britain's decision to leave the European Union immediately had an international ripple effect.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 94, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 41, \"end\": 46, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999994959733973, \"rank\": 2.806318331094139e-07, \"text\": \"Union\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"British Prime Minister David Cameron resigned, politicians in other EU countries called for their own referendums and stocks worldwide quivered, according to U.S. News & World Report.\", \"from\": 96, \"to\": 279, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But what does the decision mean for American healthcare companies?\", \"from\": 281, \"to\": 347, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Here, Dimitri Drone, global deals leader for pharmaceuticals and life sciences at PricewaterhouseCoopers, provides four thoughts on how Brexit will play out in the U.S.  1.\", \"from\": 349, \"to\": 521, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"American healthcare could be a good place to invest.\", \"from\": 522, \"to\": 574, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Regardless of international politics, people are still going to need healthcare, according to Mr. Drone, but Britain's exit provides a stronger value proposition in the U.S. as the value of the pound plummets.\", \"from\": 575, \"to\": 784, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In the short-term, the deterioration of the British pound could increase the relative value of U.S. dollar revenues, according to Mr. Drone.\", \"from\": 785, \"to\": 925, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Looking at the long-term, people will always need healthcare, so regardless, companies looking to invest should consider managed healthcare and healthcare facilities.\", \"from\": 927, \"to\": 1093, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If you know people are going to be sick and need treatment, it's a good place [for institutional investors] to think about from a long-term investment standpoint,\\\" he says.\", \"from\": 1094, \"to\": 1267, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"2.\", \"from\": 1269, \"to\": 1271, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"American healthcare companies with global operations in Europe will face challenges.\", \"from\": 1272, \"to\": 1356, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Mr. Drone says American healthcare companies with global operations in Europe - those that have at least $50 billion in market capitalization - may not necessarily see their values go down as a result of Brexit.\", \"from\": 1357, \"to\": 1568, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, they will experience challenges obtaining fundraising and regulatory approval.\", \"from\": 1569, \"to\": 1656, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"A process that was previously seamless and was able to be conducted in regular course of business now will be harder,\\\" he says.\", \"from\": 1657, \"to\": 1785, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"3.\", \"from\": 1787, \"to\": 1789, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Life sciences companies could have a harder time raising capital.\", \"from\": 1790, \"to\": 1855, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Quite a few life sciences companies are in need of constant capital replenishment.\", \"from\": 1856, \"to\": 1938, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In challening financial markets, these companies may raise capital at more expensive terms then they did prior to Brexit, says Mr. Drone.\", \"from\": 1939, \"to\": 2076, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Biotech for instance, as a sector, they will need years and years worth of capital to go from their idea to something that's a commercially viable product.\", \"from\": 2077, \"to\": 2233, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's hundreds of millions of dollars and up, so those that\\u2026do not have the most sought after technology and assets have a harder time getting financing than they did before,\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 2234, \"to\": 2420, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"4.\", \"from\": 2422, \"to\": 2424, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"M&A could be impacted.\", \"from\": 2425, \"to\": 2447, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There is always a lot of money that could be made during a period of uncertainty, meaning share prices are going to come down temporarily.\", \"from\": 2448, \"to\": 2586, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, if an American healthcare company looking to merge with or acquire another company feels bullish on the sector in the medium or long-term, the prices will rebound.\", \"from\": 2587, \"to\": 2759, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Will CEOs be more incentivized to buy something when it's on sale, when the market's down, or will they kind of look at the overall uncertainty and say, 'Even though I might be able to make some profits in the meantime, I am going to pass,'\\\" Mr. Drone says.\", \"from\": 2760, \"to\": 3018, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Which view will win out probably falls on a company-by-company level.\", \"from\": 3019, \"to\": 3089, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Some will decide not to proceed with M&A and others will decide to go after it in a more aggressive way.\\\"\", \"from\": 3090, \"to\": 3195, \"entities\": []}]}"